'''朴尚學'''（{{lang-ko|박상학}}，{{bd|1968年|2月16日}}）是[[韓國|韓國]]的[[朝鮮人權|朝鮮人權]]活動家。

朴尚學生於一個[[北韓|北韓]]特權家庭，大學畢業後在政府宣傳部門工作。”<ref name=Feith>{{cite news|last=Feith|first=David|title=Park Sang Hak: North Korea's 'Enemy Zero'|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887324853704578585961242121902.html?mod=hp_opinion|work=The Wall Street Journal|accessdate=July 7, 2013|archive-date=2013-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130812191748/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887324853704578585961242121902.html?mod=hp_opinion|dead-url=no}}</ref>1990年代後期，時值許多政府高官被肅清，出於安全考慮，經由中間人取道[[中國|中國]]前往[[韓國|韓國]]。<ref name=Hua>{{cite news|last=Hua|first=Vanessa|title=How defectors cope in South Korea / The sense of loss remains, and while life may be more free, the transition isn't easy|url=http://www.sfgate.com/news/article/How-defectors-cope-in-South-Korea-The-sense-of-2542444.php#page-2|work=Sf Gate|accessdate=July 7, 2013|date=December 20, 2006|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323133039/https://www.sfgate.com/news/article/How-defectors-cope-in-South-Korea-The-sense-of-2542444.php#page-2|dead-url=no}}</ref>2006年任[[北韓民主化運動本部|北韓民主化運動本部]]（{{朝|북한민주화운동본부}}）代表。2013年任[[自由北韓運動聯盟|自由北韓運動聯盟]]代表。<ref name=Hua /><ref>{{cite web|title=The Freedom Collection|url=http://www.freedomcollection.org/themes/why_i_became_a_dissident/park_sang_hak/|work=George W. Bush Institute|accessdate=July 7, 2013|archive-date=2016-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826212330/http://www.freedomcollection.org/themes/why_i_became_a_dissident/park_sang_hak/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

